snippet.description:
Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Mario Maker Pumpkin Head Challenge ►► http://bit.ly/1I1HYkA
Flappy Mario Maker ►► http://bit.ly/1Ney99d

Jason here. Steph and I wanted to surprise MatPat with a special birthday celebration with some of his friends and all of YOU! Alex Faciane and Jirard, the Completionist, drop by "unexpectedly" to join us in playing Mario Party, making MatPat's birthday one to remember. But ssshhh don't tell him - it's a SURPRISE!

Special Thanks to the Super Beard Bros for stopping by!
Super Beard Bros ►► http://bit.ly/1NeRadc

Follow all the updates on new episodes of GTLive!
Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive

Don't have much time but need a quick fix? Check out some of our highlight episodes for hilarious moments from our live streams. Here are a few to get you started.

HiLite: Wii Sports Ugliest Mii Ever! ►► http://bit.ly/1QqXRIA 
HiLite: MatPat Chokes in Megaman ►► http://bit.ly/1S1lFBG
HiLite: Chubby Bunny Singoff  ►► http://bit.ly/1LzAN4D
